NAME

PerlIO::Util - A selection of general PerlIO utilities

SYNOPSIS

	use PerlIO::Util;

	# to create $file if needed, and call flock($in, LOCK_EX)
	my $in = PerlIO::Util->open('+<:creat :flock', $file); 

	# to multiplex output
	STDERR->push_layer(tee => ">> $err_log");


INSTALLATION

	To install this module, run the following commands:

		perl Makefile.PL
		make
		make test
		make install


DEPENDENCIES

	Perl 5.8.0 or later, and a C compiler.

